  "description": "<p>A seriously rugged semi-soft cooler with an 18L capacity that holds lunch for your crew, with room left for beer! The tough Dryhide\u2122 shell and zipper tech is borrowed from HazMat protective gear, so it's not likely to leave a pool of sticky goo in the back of the car. Its compact shape is easy to sling over your shoulder to carry down to the beach or up the lookout.</p><ul><li>Dryhide shell is waterproof and resistant to mildew, punctures and UV rays</li><li>Liner is made from wipe-clean FDA approved food grade material</li><li>Hydrolock zipper is waterproof and airtight</li><li>Wide mouth flip top opening for easy access and visibilty of contents</li><li>Coldcell\u2122 insulation and RF welded seams keep cold in and everything else out</li><li>Double stitched webbing handles and a padded shoulder strap</li><li>Lash points for securing the cooler, or adding on accessories</li><li>Loop patch spot on the back lets you personalize your Hopper</li></ul>",
